commitResults.messageTitle: Added Level-1 functionality, Greet, Echo, Exit
Fixed cosmetic bugs and a technical bug where whitespace will result in a new prompt feedback
Added bye method for more general implementation for the end of operation of chatbot to minimise code repetition.
Added storeman method for storing of lists of input and outputting them as a list when the string list is passed as an input

Added Task Class to encapsulate tasks passed as input. Added checklist functionality and modified storeman method to accomodate new function. Added listOut method to generalise listing out of tasks, to minimise code repetition.
Added three subclasses of Task; Deadline, Event, Todo
Removed reduncant, unused checklist method
Edited Todo Class to meet specifications of project
Added support for tracking of three types of classes, Todo, Event and Deadlines
Replaced contains method with startsWith for program correctness and flexibility
Added three subclasess of Task; Todo, Event, Deadline

removed redundant, not used checklist method(checklist functionality implemented within storeman method). replaced contains with startsWith where appropariate to ensure correctness of program when running.
Various bug fix for Level-3
Change to Guard clause to ensure correctness and better flexibility of program
Bug Fix for Event TAG attribute
Added support for subclasses of Task; for Todo, Event, Deadline tracking
Added DukeException for throwing Duke-caused Exceptions

Added feature for storeman method to throw DukeException if input is unknown or in the wrong format, to be caught by main. Main will restart duke upon catching the exception and print the message of the error to console right before.
Support for delete added
updated gitignore, added test-ui-test(but to be configured to be ignored)
removed debug statement
Updated input, expected and actual as well as runtest.bat to automate the process of testing
